@startuml

actor Uporabnik
participant Angular
participant "REST API" as API
participant "Auth Service" as AUTH
database Oracle

Uporabnik -> Angular : Vnos email + geslo

Angular -> API : POST /api/auth/login

API -> AUTH : validateCredentials()

AUTH -> Oracle : preveri uporabnika

Oracle --> AUTH : podatki uporabnika

AUTH -> AUTH : generiraj JWT

AUTH --> API : JWT token

API --> Angular : Response(token)

Angular --> Uporabnik : Prijava uspešna

@enduml